Uganda, Uruguay, Zambia 
</p>
<p><i>Against</i>: 
Belgium, France, Hungary, Japan, Norway, Poland, Republic of Korea, 
Republic of Moldova, Slovakia, Spain, Ukraine, United  Kingdom of Great 
Britain and Northern Ireland, United States of America </p>


<p><b>30</b> GE.11-17043 
</p>
