Ghana, Iceland, Israel, Mauritius, Mexico, New Zealand, Nicaragua, Poland, the Republic 
of Korea, Somalia, Turkey, Ukraine, the United States of America and Venezuela 
(Bolivarian Republic of) joined the sponsors. 
