<p>754. At the 34th meeting, on 1 October 2010, the representative of South Africa 
introduced draft decision A/HRC/15/L.21, sponsored by Australia and co-sponsored by 
Nigeria, on behalf of the Group of African States. Subsequently, Albania, Andorra, 
Argentina, Armenia, Austria, Bahrain, Bangladesh, Barbados, Belarus, Belgium, Bolivia 
(Plurinational State of), Bosnia and Herzegovina, Brazil, Bulgaria, Cambodia, Canada, 
